refactor(core): modernize file processing and chunking
- Remove the `FileProcessor` class and integrate its functionalities into the `MainProcessor`. - Introduce a `ChunkProcessor` class to manage chunking and translation tasks. - Implement HTML novel format detection and extraction for improved processing of web novels. - Enhance chunking with improved language-specific sentence boundary detection. - Improve the joining of translated chunks by removing overlapping content. - Implement batch processing optimization in `_process_text_file` for improved performance. - Enhance source language detection with script analysis for better accuracy. - Modernize the codebase with type annotations and improved code structure.
Note that the HTML translation is currently experimental and very unstable!
